(
<figureCitation id="132725C82277FFB75E83F9AB3FEAA50F" box="[154,245,1551,1574]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="4.[146,173,1782,1799]" captionTargetBox="[237,1350,149,1746]" captionTargetId="figure-110@4.[235,1352,147,1747]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="Fig. 3. Adult male habitus images of Niesthrea spp. (A) N. agnes Chopra. (B) N. brevicauda Chopra. (C) N. choprai, sp. nov. (D) N. conicoloba, sp. nov. (E) N. dentata Chopra. (F) N digna Chopra. (G) N. fenestrata (Signoret). (H) N. flava Grillo and Alayo. (I) N. josei Göllner-Scheiding." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5385090" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5385090/files/figure.png" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">Figs. 3D</figureCitation>
and 
